<p><font size="12" color="#000000">Johnny Depp, the members of Guns and Roses, Donald Trump, Jon Berasategui. What links all these people? That's right, they're all in need of a good haircut. But should I be added to this list? Most likely, but why let conjecture and speculation decide when our trusty friend Revolution can do all the work? So how do we go about this? Lets find out...</font></p>
